window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><i>Nomad</i> was explosive. This is nuclear.... </p> <p>The new thriller from internationally best-selling author James Swallow. </p> <p>Move over Jason Bourne, Marc Dane is here.... </p> <p>A vicious Serbian gang whose profits come from fake nuclear weapons. A disgraced Russian general, with access to the real thing. A vengeful Somali warlord, with a cause for which he'd let the world burn. A jaded government agency, without the information to stop him. Only one man sees what's coming. And even he might not be able to prevent it.... </p> <p>Racing breathlessly from uncharted CIA prisons to the skyscrapers of Dubai, from stormbeaten oil rigs off the African coast to the ancient caverns beneath the city of Naples, Marc Dane returns in the incredible new action thriller from the internationally best-selling author of <i>Nomad</i>. </p>"; 
